n, Ludwig Erhard, Alfred Müller-Armack.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / General.2bisacsh1 aEckstein, Anja, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aEckstein, Stephan, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKnaup, Heinz, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  BWL, VWL 2005-2012z9783110345650oZDB-23-OAV0 cprintz978348658222240uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348659935040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486599350423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486599350/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GSSc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OAVc2005d2012